review_text: I have been banking here for quite a while. The branch employees are always friendly and helpful. I also see many of them involved in quite a few community events. They aren't hard-sell like the other banks trying to make you get their products whether you want to or not. When I have come in here for information about opening an account or other pertinent issues, they have always found the best fit or solution for me.

I don't bank here - Bestie does. However, I'm in here a lot, notjust with her, because they give a lot of support to the community. I'm often dropping off posters, collecting ad fees, and personally thanking employees for volunteering at different community events. I may just open an account.
